Class IngredientSet<T,M>

  • java.lang.Object

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IngredientHashSet, IngredientTreeSet

    public abstract class IngredientSet<T,M>
extends IngredientCollectionCollectionWrappedAdapter<T,M,java.util.Set<org.cyclops.commoncapabilities.api.ingredient.IngredientInstanceWrapper<T,M>>>
implements IIngredientSetMutable<T,M>
    A mutable ingredient collection using set semantics. This means that each instances can only be present once in the collection based on its equals method.
    See Also:
    Set
